</source></picture>

      
    </span>
    
  </span>
  
    <span class="e-image__meta">
      
        <figcaption>Employees David Pace, left, and Leroy Morgan load a truck with boxes to be shipped at the Amazon distribution center in Phoenix, Arizona, in November 2012. </figcaption>
      
      
